, softcover, May 2013, {{ISBNT|978-0785166948}})\n* ''Thunderbolts Volume 2: Red Scare'' (collects ''Thunderbolts'' vol. 2 #7-12, 136, softcover, October 2013, {{ISBNT|978-0785166955}})\n* ''Thunderbolts Volume 3: Infinity'' (collects ''Thunderbolts'' vol. 2 #13-19, 136, softcover, January 2014, {{ISBNT|978-0785166962}})\n* ''Thunderbolts Volume 4: No Mercy'' (collects ''Thunderbolts'' vol. 2 #20-26, 160, softcover, August 2014, {{ISBNT|978-0785189824}})\n* ''Thunderbolts Volume 5: Punisher vs. the Thunderbolts'' (collects ''Thunderbolts'' Vol. 2 27-32, 168, softcover, January 2015, {{ISBNT|978-0785189831}})\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.marvel.com/universe/Thunderbolts Thunderbolts] at Marvel.com\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20061101085525/http://www.comics101.com/archives/comics101/88.php Comics 101: Thunderbolts]\n* [http://www.marveldirectory.com/groupsandteams/thunderbolts.htm Thunderbolts] at the Marvel Directory\n* {{Comicbookdb|type=team|id=8|title=Thunderbolts}}\n* [http://www.maelmill-insi.de/UHBMCC/show.htm?SerNr=415 Thunderbolts] at the Unofficial Handbook of Marvel Comics Creators\n* {{Gcdb series|id=5812|title=Thunderbolts (1997\u20132005)}}\n* {{Gcdb series|id=12244|title=New Thunderbolts}}\n* {{Gcdb series|id=17522|title=Thunderbolts (2006\u2013present)}}\n\n{{Thunderbolts}}\n{{Black Widow}}\n{{Luke Cage}}\n{{Iron Fist}}\n{{Goblin (Marvel Comics)}}\n\n[[Category:1997 comics debuts]]\n[[Category:Characters created by Kurt Busiek]]\n[[Category:Characters created by Mark Bagley]]\n[[Category:Comics by Fabian Nicieza]]\n[[Category:Comics by Jim Zub]]\n[[Category:Comics by Kurt Busiek]]\n[[Category:Comics by Warren Ellis]]\n[[Category:Marvel Comics titles]]\n", "name_user": "Iridescent", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eCollected editions:Cleanup andtypo fixing,typo(s) fixed: 141-143 \u2192 141\u2013143 (3)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thunderbolts_(comics)"}
